error recognition
.IP "\fBmb_type\fR" 4
.IX Item "mb_type"
macroblock (\s-1MB\s0) type
.IP "\fBmmco\fR" 4
.IX Item "mmco"
memory management control operations (H.264)
.IP "\fBmv\fR" 4
.IX Item "mv"
motion vector
.IP "\fBpict\fR" 4
.IX Item "pict"
picture info
.IP "\fBpts\fR" 4
.IX Item "pts"
.PD 0
.IP "\fBqp\fR" 4
.IX Item "qp"
.PD
per-block quantization parameter (\s-1QP\s0)
.IP "\fBrc\fR" 4
.IX Item "rc"
rate control
.IP "\fBskip\fR" 4
.IX Item "skip"
.PD 0
.IP "\fBstartcode\fR" 4
.IX Item "startcode"
.IP "\fBthread_ops\fR" 4
.IX Item "thread_ops"
.PD
threading operations
.IP "\fBvis_mb_type\fR" 4
.IX Item "vis_mb_type"
visualize block types
.IP "\fBvis_qp\fR" 4
.IX Item "vis_qp"
visualize quantization parameter (\s-1QP\s0), lower \s-1QP\s0 are tinted greener
.RE
